ed68a61a4e9c7da40f4cf4c4669d1567c1c7c367.title: Calafiori & Zirkzee: David Ornstein transfers
ed68a61a4e9c7da40f4cf4c4669d1567c1c7c367.description:
Man United are working to finalise a deal for Bologna forward Joshua Zirkzee. His performances in Italy have earned him a spot in the Netherlands squad for the Euros. Arsenal have also targeted Riccardo Calafiori, could he fit in with the other defenders at the club?

So, is Zirkzee an upgrade on United’s existing forward options and could Calafiori slot into Arteta's Arsenal?

Ayo Akinwolere is joined by The Athletic's David Ornstein and Carl Anka to discuss.
